    description: `Pampers Swaddlers Size 1 diapers are the gold standard for newborn protection, trusted by millions of parents and recommended by pediatricians worldwide. These diapers feature a unique wetness indicator that changes color when it is time for a change, taking the guesswork out of diaper monitoring during those exhausting early weeks. The soft, absorbent layers lock away wetness and mess, keeping your baby's skin dry and comfortable for up to 12 hours.\n\nDesigned specifically for newborns, each Swaddlers diaper includes a gentle umbilical cord notch that protects your baby's delicate belly button area while it heals. The hypoallergenic materials are dermatologist-tested and free from harmful chemicals, making them safe even for the most sensitive skin. Pampers exclusive LockAway Channels absorb and distribute wetness evenly throughout the core, preventing leaks and blowouts.\n\nWith 198 diapers in this generous pack, you will have plenty of supply for those frequent early changes. Pampers Swaddlers wrap your baby in cloud-like softness with a fit that moves with them, whether they are sleeping soundly or kicking their legs. The color-changing wetness indicator is a game-changer for first-time parents, and the trusted Pampers name means you are choosing a product backed by decades of research and innovation in baby care.`
